{"tid":1441054,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"前線內訌係想點？？（非分化）","createTime":"2019-08-10T14:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T16:32:59.000Z","uid":226103,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"34d910b80788f8c262466f301e6350664dc546ef","tid":1441054,"uid":226103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:45:16.000Z","msg":"我唔想做分化撚<br />\n但真心前線可唔可以唔好成日鬧交<br />\n上次85係北角鬧左一次<br />\n嘈話要唔要返新光定留北角狗屋<br />\n今日係沙田同牛頭角又鬧多次<br />\n我唔覺得個啲係鬼<br />\n應該都係太躁底衰衝動<br />\n但真係嘈得多你地會俾人屌你地係鬼想搞分化<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該你地唔好再鬧交</span></span><br />\n鬧到好多手足其實好無癮<br />\n最後每次轉場都會少一堆人<br />\n而且聽你地鬧交又好無意思<br />\n不如大家冷靜少少做賽後檢討好過<br />\n有商有量<br />\n小弟每次都跟你地留到最後<br />\n但今日真係一返到德福就聽到你地嘈交好無癮<br />\n尤其係今日係大圍仲有人想打交話要隻抽<br />\n我個時心諗屌你香蕉糖咩？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地之所以拖到咁耐打到咁耐就係因為我地團結</span></span><br />\n你地鬧交真係會鬧走好多人覺得你地無意思<br />\n求下各位大佬<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再屌人老母鬧交</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00abcc3bb168f4023dfbb7f53cd9fff07486124","tid":1441054,"uid":226103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:45:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7bab80c7de331b00d4a64c4e58703ecb225ae8be","tid":1441054,"uid":226103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:45:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e28d4b77ac102354e8a711633b75ec9274de955b","tid":1441054,"uid":226103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:45:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e2817f4bd5ca15c5d43f34aeeec06f97fb9871e","tid":1441054,"uid":226103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1